QuestData.Title: Maintenance Mode
QuestData.Description:
The architect set forth these tasks:
Stay safe.
Restore the Protoform Repository when danger passes.
The mortal knows the cyphers. The mortal will help with the tasks.
Attuning of the energy terminals is required. Each terminal requires a codex. Invaders pilfered the necessary codices.
Go.
QuestData.LogDescription: Attune $1oa Energy Terminals in the Arrangement Index.
QuestData.QuestCompletionLog: Speak to Kodah in the Protoform Repository.
